# 🌍 Language Detection using Machine Learning

This project uses a machine learning model to detect the language of a given text input. It supports 22 languages including English, Urdu, Arabic, Chinese, Hindi, French, Spanish, Turkish, and more.

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Supports **22 languages**
- ✅ Uses **TF-IDF (character-level)** for robust feature extraction
- ✅ Trained with **Multinomial Naive Bayes** classifier
- ✅ Includes **confidence-based prediction** to detect unknown languages
- ✅ Achieves **98% accuracy** on the test dataset

